---
---

<section class="problem" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem-inner">

      <div class="problem-statement fade-up">
        <span class="label">The Problem</span>
        <h2 id="problem-heading">Most diets fail because they lack structure.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-body fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
        <p>
          Eating "healthy" isn't enough. Switching diets doesn't work. The real problem?
          Your nutrition never matches your goal. CutPhase gives you a clear system so
          every meal moves you forward.
        </p>

        <ul class="problem-list" aria-label="Common diet problems">
          <li>
            <span class="problem-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            No clear goal behind what you eat
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="problem-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Generic plans that don't adapt to your phase
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="problem-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Progress that stalls with no direction
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    padding-block: var(--section-pad);
    background-color: var(--bg-alt);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .problem-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .problem-statement h2 {
    max-width: 400px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .problem-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    max-width: 400px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .problem-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .problem-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--muted-dim);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .problem-indicator {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--muted-dim);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .problem-statement h2,
    .problem-body p {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
